n style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\">M\\u1eb7c d&ugrave; s\\u1ebd g\\u1eb7p nhi\\u1ec1u th&aacute;ch th\\u1ee9c kh&ocirc;ng nh\\u1ecf t\\u1eeb n\\u1ec1n ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i c\\u1ee7a c&aacute;c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n tr&ecirc;n th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi nh\\u01b0 M\\u1ef9, EU, &Uacute;c c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 l&agrave;m thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i c\\u1ea5u tr&uacute;c th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u01b0ng ng&agrave;nh ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c d\\u1ef1 \\u0111o&aacute;n s\\u1ebd c&oacute; t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng m\\u1ea1nh theo h\\u01b0\\u1edbng c&ocirc;ng nghi\\u1ec7p v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n h&oacute;a cao giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2016-2020.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\">Song song v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n nhanh c\\u1ee7a xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i c&ocirc;ng nghi\\u1ec7p l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 gia t\\u0103ng &aacute;p l\\u1ef1c v\\u1ec1 d\\u1ecbch b\\u1ec7nh, l\\u1ea1m d\\u1ee5ng kh&aacute;ng sinh trong ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i v&agrave; nu&ocirc;i tr\\u1ed3ng th\\u1ee7y s\\u1ea3n.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\">Gi\\u1ea3i ph&aacute;p n&agrave;o \\u0111\\u1ec3 n&acirc;ng cao s\\u1ee9c c\\u1ea1nh tranh cho s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam v\\u1edbi th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi?<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\">D&ograve;ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m TACA \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u01b0a ra th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng v&agrave; mang l\\u1ea1i gi&aacute; tr\\u1ecb to l\\u1edbn cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; m&aacute;y s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n v&agrave; h\\u1ed9 ch\\u0103n nu&ocirc;i<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\">Th\\u1ee9 1 c&aacute;c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m TACA gi&uacute;p cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; m&aacute;y s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5